#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:1
msgid "Multi-Model Setup and Fallback Chains"
msgstr "Configuración de múltiples modelos y cadenas de respaldo"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:3
msgid ""
"A walkthrough of the common patterns for using multiple model providers: "
"cost optimisation, quality tiers, local-first with hosted fallback, API key "
"rotation, and rate-limit resilience."
msgstr "Un recorrido por los patrones comunes para usar múltiples proveedores de modelos: optimización de costos, niveles de calidad, enfoque local con respaldo en la nube, rotación de claves de API y resiliencia ante límites de tasa."

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:5
msgid "**Reference material** for the provider system lives in:"
msgstr "El **material de referencia** para el sistema del proveedor se encuentra en:"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:6
msgid ""
"[Model Providers → Overview](../providers/overview.md) — what providers are, "
"configuration shape"
msgstr "[Proveedores de modelos → Descripción general](../providers/overview.md) — qué son los proveedores, forma de configuración"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:7
msgid ""
"[Model Providers → Fallback & routing](../providers/fallback-and-routing.md) "
"— `reliable` and `router` meta-providers"
msgstr "[Proveedores de modelos → Fallback y enrutamiento](../providers/fallback-and-routing.md) — meta-proveedores `reliable` y `router`"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:8
msgid ""
"[Model Providers → Catalog](../providers/catalog.md) — every provider's "
"config shape"
msgstr "[Proveedores de modelos → Catálogo](../providers/catalog.md) — la forma de configuración de cada proveedor"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:10
msgid "When to Use Multi-Model Setup"
msgstr "Cuándo usar una configuración de múltiples modelos"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:12
msgid "Multi-model configuration is useful for:"
msgstr "La configuración de múltiples modelos es útil para:"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:14
msgid ""
"**High reliability**: Automatically fall back to alternative providers when "
"the primary fails"
msgstr ""
"**Alta fiabilidad**: Cambia automáticamente a proveedores alternativos "
"cuando el principal falla"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:15
msgid ""
"**Cost optimization**: Route expensive models through fallback chains for "
"rate-limited scenarios"
msgstr ""
"**Optimización de costos**: Enruta modelos costosos a través de cadenas de "
"respaldo para escenarios con límites de tasa"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:16
msgid ""
"**Regional resilience**: Use geographically distributed providers to handle "
"region-specific outages"
msgstr ""
"**Resiliencia regional**: Utiliza proveedores distribuidos geográficamente "
"para gestionar las interrupciones específicas de cada región."

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:17
msgid ""
"**Capability flexibility**: Try different models when one lacks required "
"features (e.g., tool calling, vision)"
msgstr ""
"**Flexibilidad de capacidades**: Prueba diferentes modelos cuando uno "
"carezca de las características necesarias (por ejemplo, llamada de "
"herramientas, visión)."

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:18
msgid ""
"**Rate limit handling**: Rotate through API keys on `429` (rate limit) "
"responses"
msgstr ""
"**Manejo de límites de tasa**: Rota las claves de API en las respuestas "
"`429` (límite de tasa)"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:19
msgid ""
"**Development and testing**: Switch between cloud and local models without "
"code changes"
msgstr ""
"**Desarrollo y pruebas**: Cambia entre modelos en la nube y locales sin "
"realizar cambios en el código"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:21
msgid "Core Concepts"
msgstr "Conceptos principales"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:23
msgid "Fallback Provider Chains"
msgstr "Cadenas de proveedores de respaldo"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:25
msgid ""
"When a provider experiences a transient error (timeout, connection failure, "
"auth issue), ZeroClaw automatically attempts fallback providers in the order "
"specified."
msgstr ""
"Cuando un proveedor experimenta un error transitorio (timeout, fallo de "
"conexión, problema de autenticación), ZeroClaw intenta automáticamente los "
"proveedores de respaldo en el orden especificado."

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:27
msgid ""
"**Example**: If your primary provider is `openai` but it's temporarily "
"unavailable, ZeroClaw can automatically fall back to `anthropic`, then "
"`groq`."
msgstr ""
"**Ejemplo**: Si tu proveedor principal es `openai` pero está temporalmente "
"no disponible, ZeroClaw puede automáticamente hacer una transición a "
"`anthropic`, luego a `groq`."

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:29
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[reliability]\n"
"fallback_providers = [\"anthropic\", \"groq\", \"openrouter\"]\n"
"```"
msgstr ""
"```toml\n"
"[reliability]\n"
"fallback_providers = [\"anthropic\", \"groq\", \"openrouter\"]\n"
"```"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:34
msgid ""
"When the primary provider recovers, ZeroClaw resumes using it (no sticky "
"failover)."
msgstr ""
"Cuando el proveedor principal se recupera, ZeroClaw reanuda su uso (sin "
"failover persistente)."

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:36
msgid "Model-Level Fallbacks"
msgstr "Fallbacks a nivel de modelo"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:38
msgid ""
"Some models may not be available in all regions, or you might want to use a "
"faster model when a heavy model is rate-limited."
msgstr ""
"Algunos modelos pueden no estar disponibles en todas las regiones, o quizás "
"quieras usar un modelo más rápido cuando un modelo pesado esté sujeto a "
"límites de tasa."

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:40
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[reliability]\n"
"model_fallbacks = { \"claude-opus-4-7\" = [\"claude-sonnet-4-6\", \"gpt-4o"
"\"] }\n"
"```"
msgstr ""
"```toml\n"
"[reliability]\n"
"model_fallbacks = { \"claude-opus-4-7\" = [\"claude-sonnet-4-6\", \"gpt-4o"
"\"] }\n"
"```"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:45
msgid ""
"If `claude-opus-4-7` fails or is unavailable, ZeroClaw tries the fallback "
"models in order while staying within the same provider (unless a provider-"
"level fallback is also configured)."
msgstr ""
"Si `claude-opus-4-7` falla o no está disponible, ZeroClaw intenta los "
"modelos de respaldo en orden, manteniéndose dentro del mismo proveedor (a "
"menos que también se haya configurado un respaldo a nivel de proveedor)."

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:47
msgid "API Key Rotation"
msgstr "Rotación de claves API"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:49
msgid ""
"For providers that frequently encounter rate limits, you can supply "
"additional API keys that ZeroClaw will rotate through on `429` responses."
msgstr ""
"Para los proveedores que frecuentemente encuentran límites de tasa, puedes "
"proporcionar claves de API adicionales que ZeroClaw rotará en las respuestas "
"`429`."

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:51
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[reliability]\n"
"api_keys = [\"sk-key-2\", \"sk-key-3\", \"sk-key-4\"]\n"
"```"
msgstr ""
"```toml\n"
"[reliability]\n"
"api_keys = [\"sk-key-2\", \"sk-key-3\", \"sk-key-4\"]\n"
"```"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:56
msgid ""
"The primary `api_key` (configured globally or per-channel) is always tried "
"first; these extras are rotated on rate-limit errors."
msgstr ""
"La `api_key` principal (configurada globalmente o por canal) siempre se "
"intenta primero; estos extras se rotan en caso de errores de límite de tasa."

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:58
msgid "Provider Retries"
msgstr "Reintentos del proveedor"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:60
msgid ""
"Each provider attempt includes configurable retries with exponential backoff "
"before moving to the next fallback."
msgstr ""
"Cada intento del proveedor incluye reintentos configurables con retroceso "
"exponencial antes de pasar al siguiente fallback."

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:68
msgid "Configuration Structure"
msgstr "Estructura de configuración"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:70
msgid ""
"All multi-model behavior lives under the `[reliability]` section of `config."
"toml`. See the [Config reference](../reference/config.md) for the full field "
"index and defaults."
msgstr ""
"Todo el comportamiento multimodelo se encuentra en la sección "
"`[reliability]` de `config.toml`. Consulta la [Referencia de configuración]"
"(../reference/config.md) para obtener el índice completo de campos y los "
"valores predeterminados."

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:72
msgid "Example Configurations"
msgstr "Ejemplos de configuraciones"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:74
msgid "Basic Fallback Chain"
msgstr "Cadena básica de respaldo"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:76
msgid "Set up a simple fallback from your primary provider to a backup:"
msgstr ""
"Configura un simple respaldo desde tu proveedor principal a uno de respaldo:"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:78
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"default_provider = \"openai\"\n"
"default_model = \"gpt-4o\"\n"
"\n"
"[reliability]\n"
"fallback_providers = [\"anthropic\"]\n"
"```"
msgstr ""
"```toml\n"
"default_provider = \"openai\"\n"
"default_model = \"gpt-4o\"\n"
"\n"
"[reliability]\n"
"fallback_providers = [\"anthropic\"]\n"
"```"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:86
msgid ""
"**Behavior**: If OpenAI times out or returns an error, ZeroClaw will retry "
"twice with exponential backoff, then attempt the same request using "
"Anthropic."
msgstr ""
"**Comportamiento**: Si OpenAI supera el tiempo de espera o devuelve un "
"error, ZeroClaw reintentará dos veces con retroceso exponencial y luego "
"intentará la misma solicitud utilizando Anthropic."

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:88
msgid "High-Reliability Multi-Provider Setup"
msgstr "Configuración de Alta Disponibilidad con Múltiples Proveedores"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:90
msgid "Combine provider fallbacks with model fallbacks and API key rotation:"
msgstr ""
"Combina las opciones de respaldo del proveedor con las opciones de respaldo "
"del modelo y la rotación de claves de API:"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:92
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"default_provider = \"openai\"\n"
"default_model = \"gpt-4o\"\n"
"api_key = \"sk-openai-primary\"\n"
"\n"
"[reliability]\n"
"fallback_providers = [\"anthropic\", \"groq\", \"openrouter\"]\n"
"api_keys = [\"sk-openai-backup-1\", \"sk-openai-backup-2\"]\n"
"\n"
"[reliability.model_fallbacks]\n"
"\"gpt-4o\" = [\"gpt-4-turbo\", \"gpt-3.5-turbo\"]\n"
"\"gpt-4-turbo\" = [\"gpt-3.5-turbo\"]\n"
"```"
msgstr ""
"```toml\n"
"default_provider = \"openai\"\n"
"default_model = \"gpt-4o\"\n"
"api_key = \"sk-openai-primary\"\n"
"\n"
"[reliability]\n"
"fallback_providers = [\"anthropic\", \"groq\", \"openrouter\"]\n"
"api_keys = [\"sk-openai-backup-1\", \"sk-openai-backup-2\"]\n"
"\n"
"[reliability.model_fallbacks]\n"
"\"gpt-4o\" = [\"gpt-4-turbo\", \"gpt-3.5-turbo\"]\n"
"\"gpt-4-turbo\" = [\"gpt-3.5-turbo\"]\n"
"```"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:106
msgid "**Behavior**:"
msgstr "**Comportamiento**:"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:107
msgid "Try OpenAI `gpt-4o` with primary key (2 retries)"
msgstr "Prueba OpenAI `gpt-4o` con la clave principal (2 reintentos)"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:108
msgid "On rate-limit, rotate to backup API keys"
msgstr "En caso de límite de tasa, cambiar a claves de API de respaldo"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:109
msgid ""
"If OpenAI still fails, fall back to Anthropic with same model request "
"(Anthropic will select available equivalent)"
msgstr ""
"Si OpenAI sigue fallando, vuelve a Anthropic con la misma solicitud de "
"modelo (Anthropic seleccionará el equivalente disponible)."

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:110
msgid "If Anthropic unavailable, try Groq, then OpenRouter"
msgstr ""
"Si Anthropic no está disponible, prueba con Groq y luego con OpenRouter."

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:111
msgid "If model not available, try fallback models in order"
msgstr ""
"Si el modelo no está disponible, intenta usar los modelos de respaldo en "
"orden"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:113
msgid "Local Development with Cloud Fallback"
msgstr "Desarrollo local con respaldo en la nube"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:115
msgid "Use a local Ollama instance as primary, fall back to cloud provider:"
msgstr ""
"Utiliza una instancia local de Ollama como principal y, en caso de fallo, "
"recurre a un proveedor en la nube:"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:117
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"default_provider = \"ollama\"\n"
"default_model = \"llama2:70b\"\n"
"api_url = \"http://localhost:11434\"\n"
"\n"
"[reliability]\n"
"fallback_providers = [\"openrouter\", \"groq\"]\n"
"```"
msgstr ""
"```toml\n"
"default_provider = \"ollama\"\n"
"default_model = \"llama2:70b\"\n"
"api_url = \"http://localhost:11434\"\n"
"\n"
"[reliability]\n"
"fallback_providers = [\"openrouter\", \"groq\"]\n"
"```"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:126
msgid ""
"**Behavior**: If Ollama goes down or times out, automatically use OpenRouter "
"or Groq instead without configuration changes."
msgstr ""
"**Comportamiento**: Si Ollama se cae o supera el tiempo de espera, utiliza "
"automáticamente OpenRouter o Groq en su lugar sin necesidad de cambios en la "
"configuración."

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:128
msgid "Cost Optimization: Heavy Model with Fast Fallback"
msgstr "Optimización de costos: Modelo pesado con fallback rápido"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:130
msgid ""
"Use an expensive reasoning model for complex tasks, but fall back to a "
"faster model:"
msgstr ""
"Utiliza un modelo de razonamiento costoso para tareas complejas, pero "
"recurre a un modelo más rápido:"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:132
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"default_provider = \"anthropic\"\n"
"default_model = \"claude-opus-4-7\"\n"
"\n"
"[reliability]\n"
"model_fallbacks = { \"claude-opus-4-7\" = [\"claude-sonnet-4-6\"] }\n"
"```"
msgstr ""
"```toml\n"
"default_provider = \"anthropic\"\n"
"default_model = \"claude-opus-4-7\"\n"
"\n"
"[reliability]\n"
"model_fallbacks = { \"claude-opus-4-7\" = [\"claude-sonnet-4-6\"] }\n"
"```"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:140
msgid ""
"**Behavior**: When Opus is rate-limited or slow, automatically use Sonnet "
"(typically 2–3x faster and cheaper)."
msgstr ""
"**Comportamiento**: Cuando Opus está limitado por la velocidad o es lento, "
"utiliza automáticamente Sonnet (generalmente 2–3 veces más rápido y "
"económico)."

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:142
msgid "Multi-Region Setup"
msgstr "Configuración de múltiples regiones"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:144
msgid "For organizations with multi-region deployments:"
msgstr "Para organizaciones con implementaciones en múltiples regiones:"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:146
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"# Primary US region\n"
"default_provider = \"anthropic\"\n"
"default_model = \"claude-sonnet-4-6\"\n"
"\n"
"[reliability]\n"
"# Fall back to EU region provider if US Anthropic is down\n"
"fallback_providers = [\"bedrock\"]  # AWS Bedrock in multiple regions\n"
"provider_retries = 3\n"
"provider_backoff_ms = 1000\n"
"```"
msgstr ""
"```toml\n"
"# Región principal de EE. UU.\n"
"default_provider = \"anthropic\"\n"
"default_model = \"claude-sonnet-4-6\"\n"
"\n"
"[reliability]\n"
"# Recurrir al proveedor de la región de la UE si Anthropic en EE. UU. no "
"está disponible\n"
"fallback_providers = [\"bedrock\"]  # AWS Bedrock en múltiples regiones\n"
"provider_retries = 3\n"
"provider_backoff_ms = 1000\n"
"```"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:158
msgid "Ensure each fallback provider has credentials in your environment:"
msgstr ""
"Asegúrate de que cada proveedor de respaldo tenga credenciales en tu entorno:"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:161
#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:162
#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:163 src/channels/acp.md:56
#: src/channels/acp.md:57
msgid "\"...\""
msgstr "\"...\""

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:166
msgid "Hot Reload Behavior"
msgstr "Comportamiento de Recarga Rápida"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:168
msgid ""
"The `[reliability]` section is hot-reloadable. While a channel or gateway is "
"running, updates to `config.toml` take effect on the next inbound message "
"without requiring a restart."
msgstr ""
"La sección `[reliability]` es recargable en caliente. Mientras un canal o "
"puerta de enlace está en ejecución, las actualizaciones en `config.toml` "
"surten efecto en el siguiente mensaje entrante sin necesidad de reiniciar."

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:170
msgid "Error Handling and Fallback Triggers"
msgstr "Manejo de errores y activadores de respaldo"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:172
msgid "Fallback is triggered by:"
msgstr "El fallback se activa por:"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:174
msgid "**Timeout**: Provider did not respond within the configured timeout"
msgstr ""
"**Tiempo de espera agotado**: El proveedor no respondió dentro del tiempo de "
"espera configurado"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:175
msgid "**Connection error**: Network/DNS failure"
msgstr "**Error de conexión**: Fallo de red/DNS"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:176
msgid ""
"**Auth error**: Invalid credentials (retries only if transient auth service "
"issues detected)"
msgstr ""
"**Error de autenticación**: Credenciales no válidas (solo se reintenta si se "
"detectan problemas transitorios del servicio de autenticación)"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:177
msgid ""
"**Rate limit (429)**: HTTP 429; triggers API key rotation first, then "
"provider fallback"
msgstr ""
"**Límite de tasa (429)**: HTTP 429; activa primero la rotación de la clave "
"de API y luego el cambio de proveedor"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:178
msgid "**Service unavailable (503)**: Temporary service issue"
msgstr "**Servicio no disponible (503)**: Problema temporal del servicio"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:179
msgid "**Model not found**: Triggers model fallback chain if configured"
msgstr ""
"**Modelo no encontrado**: Activa la cadena de respaldo del modelo si está "
"configurada"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:181
msgid "Fallback is **not** triggered by:"
msgstr "El **fallback** no se activa por:"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:183
msgid "**Invalid request (400)**: Malformed input; retrying won't help"
msgstr ""
"**Solicitud no válida (400)**: Entrada malformada; reintentar no ayudará"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:184
msgid "**Permanent auth failure**: Invalid API key format"
msgstr "**Error de autenticación permanente**: Formato de clave API no válido"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:185
msgid "**Model output errors**: The model responded but returned an error"
msgstr ""
"**Errores de salida del modelo**: El modelo respondió pero devolvió un error"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:187
msgid "Debugging Fallback Activity"
msgstr "Depuración de la actividad de respaldo"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:189
msgid "Enable runtime traces to debug fallback behavior:"
msgstr ""
"Habilitar trazas en tiempo de ejecución para depurar el comportamiento de "
"respaldo:"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:191
msgid ""
"```toml\n"
"[observability]\n"
"runtime_trace_mode = \"rolling\"\n"
"runtime_trace_path = \"state/runtime-trace.jsonl\"\n"
"```"
msgstr ""
"```toml\n"
"[observabilidad]\n"
"modo_rastro_ejecucion = \"rodante\"\n"
"ruta_rastro_ejecucion = \"state/runtime-trace.jsonl\"\n"
"```"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:197
msgid "Then query traces:"
msgstr "Luego, consulta los rastros:"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:200
msgid "# Show all fallback events\n"
msgstr "# Mostrar todos los eventos de respaldo\n"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:201
msgid "\"fallback\""
msgstr "\"fallback\""

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:202
msgid "# Show provider retry details\n"
msgstr "# Mostrar detalles de reintento del proveedor\n"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:204
msgid "\"provider\""
msgstr "\"proveedor\""

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:205
msgid "# Show rate-limit rotation\n"
msgstr "# Mostrar rotación de límite de tasa\n"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:207
msgid "\"429\""
msgstr "\"429\""

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:210
msgid "Best Practices"
msgstr "Mejores prácticas"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:212
msgid ""
"**Order by reliability**: Put most reliable providers first in "
"`fallback_providers`"
msgstr ""
"**Ordenar por fiabilidad**: Coloca los proveedores más confiables primero en "
"`fallback_providers`."

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:213
msgid ""
"**Test fallback chains**: Verify fallback behavior before production use"
msgstr ""
"**Probar cadenas de respaldo**: Verificar el comportamiento de respaldo "
"antes de su uso en producción"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:214
msgid ""
"**Monitor API key rotation**: Track rate-limit events to know when rotation "
"is active"
msgstr ""
"**Monitorizar la rotación de la clave API**: Rastrear eventos de límite de "
"tasa para saber cuándo está activa la rotación"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:215
msgid ""
"**Keep model fallbacks semantically similar**: Don't fall back from a "
"reasoning model to a chat model without intention"
msgstr ""
"**Mantén las alternativas del modelo semánticamente similares**: No cambies "
"de un modelo de razonamiento a un modelo de chat sin intención"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:216
msgid ""
"**Use environment variables**: Store sensitive API keys in env, not config"
msgstr ""
"**Usa variables de entorno**: Almacena las claves API sensibles en variables "
"de entorno, no en archivos de configuración."

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:217
msgid ""
"**Document fallback intent**: Add comments in config explaining why each "
"fallback exists"
msgstr ""
"**Intención de respaldo del documento**: Agrega comentarios en la "
"configuración explicando por qué existe cada respaldo."

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:218
msgid ""
"**Verify multi-model credentials**: Ensure all fallback providers have valid "
"credentials set"
msgstr ""
"**Verificar las credenciales de múltiples modelos**: Asegúrate de que todos "
"los proveedores de respaldo tengan credenciales válidas configuradas"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:220
msgid "Credential Resolution"
msgstr "Resolución de credenciales"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:222
msgid ""
"Each fallback provider resolves credentials independently using the standard "
"resolution order:"
msgstr ""
"Cada proveedor de respaldo resuelve las credenciales de forma independiente "
"utilizando el orden de resolución estándar:"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:224
msgid "Explicit credential from config/CLI"
msgstr "Credenciales explícitas desde la configuración/CLI"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:225
msgid "Provider-specific environment variable"
msgstr "Variable de entorno específica del proveedor"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:226
msgid "Generic fallback: `ZEROCLAW_API_KEY`, then `API_KEY`"
msgstr "Valor predeterminado genérico: `ZEROCLAW_API_KEY`, luego `API_KEY`"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:228
msgid ""
"**Important**: The primary provider's API key is not automatically reused by "
"fallback providers. Set credentials for each provider separately."
msgstr ""
"**Importante**: La clave API del proveedor principal no se reutiliza "
"automáticamente por los proveedores de respaldo. Establezca las credenciales "
"para cada proveedor por separado."

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:230 src/sop/connectivity.md:51
msgid "Example:"
msgstr "Ejemplo:"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:233
msgid "\"sk-...\""
msgstr "\"sk-...\""

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:234
msgid "\"claude-...\""
msgstr "\"claude-...\""

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:235
msgid "\"gsk-...\""
msgstr "\"gsk-...\""

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:238
msgid "Limits and Constraints"
msgstr "Límites y restricciones"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:240
msgid ""
"Maximum fallback providers: Limited by configuration file size (typically "
"100+ chains are supported)"
msgstr ""
"Proveedores de respaldo máximo: Limitado por el tamaño del archivo de "
"configuración (generalmente se admiten más de 100 cadenas)"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:241
msgid "Maximum model fallbacks per model: No hard limit"
msgstr "Caídas máximas del modelo por modelo: Sin límite estricto"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:242
msgid "API key rotation: All keys are tried before timing out"
msgstr ""
"Rotación de claves API: Se prueban todas las claves antes de agotar el "
"tiempo de espera"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:243
msgid "Retry attempts: Configurable per provider with exponential backoff"
msgstr ""
"Intentos de reintento: Configurables por proveedor con retroceso exponencial"

#: src/getting-started/multi-model-setup.md:244
msgid ""
"Total timeout budget: Cumulative across retries and fallbacks; channel-level "
"timeout still applies"
msgstr ""
"Presupuesto total de tiempo de espera: Acumulado entre reintentos y "
