msgstr "`--level <LEVEL>` — Nivel utilizado al activar el estop desde `zeroclaw estop`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:478
msgid ""
"Possible values: `kill-all`, `network-kill`, `domain-block`, `tool-freeze`"
msgstr "Valores posibles: `kill-all`, `network-kill`, `domain-block`, `tool-freeze`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:480
msgid ""
"`--domain <DOMAINS>` — Domain pattern(s) for `domain-block` (repeatable)"
msgstr "`--domain <DOMINIOS>` — Patrón(es) de dominio para `domain-block` (repetible)"

#: src/reference/cli.md:481
msgid "`--tool <TOOLS>` — Tool name(s) for `tool-freeze` (repeatable)"
msgstr "`--tool <TOOLS>` — Nombre(s) de la(s) herramienta(s) para `tool-freeze` (repetible)"

#: src/reference/cli.md:485
