"Is there a clear acceptance criteria? Does it need an ADR or design note? Is "
"the risk tier assigned?"
msgstr "¿Hay criterios de aceptación claros? ¿Se necesita un ADR o una nota de diseño? ¿Se ha asignado el nivel de riesgo?"

#: src/foundations/fnd-003-governance.md:111
msgid "Assignee + reviewer"
msgstr "Asignado + revisor"

#: src/foundations/fnd-003-governance.md:112
msgid "Defined → In Progress"
msgstr "Definido → En progreso"

#: src/foundations/fnd-003-governance.md:112
msgid ""
"Is there an assignee? Is it sized? Are the related ADRs or docs identified?"
msgstr "¿Hay un asignado? ¿Está dimensionado? ¿Se han identificado los ADR o documentos relacionados?"

#: src/foundations/fnd-003-governance.md:112
msgid "Assignee"
msgstr "Asignado"

#: src/foundations/fnd-003-governance.md:113
msgid "In Progress → In Review"
msgstr "En progreso → En revisión"

#: src/foundations/fnd-003-governance.md:113
msgid ""
"Do tests exist for the new behavior? Is CI passing? Is the PR description "
